Validate URLs before rendering as <a href>. Accept only 'https://' scheme:

  def safe_link(url, label='link'):
      import html
      if url and url.startswith('https://'):
          return f'<a href="{html.escape(url)}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{label}</a>'
      return html.escape(url) if url else '—'
